text: Cristina Gomez (born 6 July 1998 in San Pedro del Pinatar) is a Spanish professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 97 in the world. She is in Spain women's national squash team. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish female squash players Category:Competitors at the 2017 World Games
